effect:
Choose a _Major Attack_ with a _Charged Effect_. Instead of immediately making the _Attack_, instead create a _Hazard_ equal to the _Area_ the _Charged Effect_ would Target (a single space within _Range_ if no Area is listed). End your _Turn_, then become _Charging_.
&nbsp;
At the end of the next _Phase_ remove _Charging_ and the _Hazard_, then resolve the _Attack_ against all creatures in the _Area_. You may choose to not make this _Attack_ and instead gain 1 _Momentum_ and resolve the _On Miss_ effect when removing the _Hazard_.
